Package com.dselent.bigarraylist

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BigArrayList<E>
    A BigArrayList acts the same way a regular ArrayList would for data sizes that cannot fit in memory all at once.
    CacheMapping<E>
    Class that manages the mapping from files on disk to elements in memory for the BigArrayList class.
    FileAccessor<E>
    Class that reads and writes the contents of the BigArrayList to/from disk.
    SoftMapping<E>
    Class that manages the mapping from virtual indices to physical indices in memory Since the remove operation is coalesced some elements are not physically removed until later.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BigArrayList.IOTypes
    Possible IO serialization types
